article.description: — Joey Reilly had 23 points in Sacred Heart's 80-73 win against Le Moyne on Monday night.
article.headline: Reilly scores 23, Sacred Heart beats Le Moyne 80-73
article.linkText: Reilly scores 23, Sacred Heart beats Le Moyne 80-73
article.story: SYRACUSE, N.Y. -- — Joey Reilly had 23 points in Sacred Heart's 80-73 win against Le Moyne on Monday night. Reilly shot 7 for 9 (5 for 6 from 3-point range) and 4 of 4 from the free throw line for the Pioneers (9-10, 3-1 Northeast Conference). Aidan Carpenter scored 20 points while going 7 of 13 from the floor, including 1 for 6 from 3-point range, and 5 for 6 from the line. Alex Sobel had nine points and was 3 of 6 shooting and 3 of 4 from the free throw line. Kaiyem Cleary led the way for the Dolphins (6-11, 1-2) with 19 points and 11 rebounds. Darrick Jones Jr. added 10 points for Le Moyne. In addition, Nathan McClure finished with nine points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
